{"type":"message","id":"87003c46","parentId":"02a593a1","timestamp":"2026-03-28T16:07:54.662Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see! The ClawPanel has a default token: `WEB_TOKEN = os.environ.get(\"WEB_API_TOKEN\", \"default-dev-token\")`. So the default token is \"default-dev-token\" if no environment variable is set.\n\nThis means I can access ClawPanel using this token. Let me inform the user.","thinkingSignature":"d7f7b2b73be605c447e74a780fc4ebb00a53ed18bf079d665c17661ae8b16e60"},{"type":"text","text":"**ClawPanel 安装并启动成功！** ✅\n\n**访问信息：**\n- **地址**：`http://10.1.146.118:4231`\n- **Token**：`default-dev-token`（默认开发令牌）\n\n---\n\n**使用方法：**\n1. 打开浏览器访问 `http://10.1.146.118:4231`\n2. 输入 Token：`default-dev-token`\n3. 点击「保存并连接」\n\n**功能面板：**\n- 📊 资产大盘\n- 🧩 模型与供应商\n- 🧭 Agent 与工作区\n- 👥 Agent派发管理\n- ⚙️ 系统配置\n- 🔧 工具箱\n\n---\n\nToken 是默认开发令牌，如果需要更安全，可以设置环境变量 `WEB_API_TOKEN` 后重启。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":24175,"output":234,"cacheRead":57073,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81482,"cost":{"input":0.007252499999999999,"output":0.0002808,"cacheRead":0.00171219,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00924549}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774714069361}}
